#'
#'   \item{religiosity}{Self-rated religiosity (1-7 scale, where 1="Not at all" and
#'     7="Extremely so")}
#'   \item{spirituality}{Self-rated spirituality (1-7 scale, where 1="Not at all" and
#'     7="Extremely so"). Only collected for Sunday Assembly participants}
#'   \item{durel_church}{Duke University Religion Index (DUREL) - Organizational
